data.title: Daytime is not the right tome
data.text: Stopped in during lunch. Incredibly slow for soup and sandwiches. Of course they have beer which is good, it's a bar. Won't stop again though.

data.title: New place to stop while in Peoria
data.text:
Was in town for a local concert was a big early decided to stop in for a drink to kill some time. So glad we did!

The service was great. The atmosphere was good too. Plenty of seating and bar games around the room

The prices were seriously cheap and will be the place we go next time we stay in Peoria

The bathrooms were the only down to this place and why its a 3 not a 4 

Both the men and the women's rooms looked like a scene out if a horror flick to the point you didn't want to use it in the case you might catch something. The guys room door doesn't lock and is a single stall.  The women's room looked like someone's head went through the wall

Over all cool place and hope to be back
